Parts
 -Directory Parser

Documentation
 
------------------------------
/incoming = where the original ~4000 releases will be stored before being parsed, relocated and into mysql. also /incoming is where i will upload new releases to be processed (cron)

for each directory
 store original release name (original folder name)
 store pretty release name with correct capitalization, no -groupname and no .'s or _'s
 store filenames inside of each directory where you'll know the name to link for the download and the .nfo for the viewer
 mv original folder + contents from /incoming to /archive

/archive = where releases will go after beinged processed from /incoming.  also, this is where the download script will send the file from
